    "name": "救援测验",
    "steam_appid": 3270510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >救援测验》是一款自上而下的救援益智动作游戏，在游戏中，你和你的救援伙伴要执行一项任务，营救遇险人员。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/b029ba05648398614f5b5c049cdbde9a.poster.avif?t=1745087539\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/b029ba05648398614f5b5c049cdbde9a.webm?t=1745087539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/b029ba05648398614f5b5c049cdbde9a.mp4?t=1745087539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在营救过程中，巴迪会被各种地形和噱头阻挡。 您要帮助好友克服地形和障碍，为救援人员铺平道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/ed611d80a98dd7737e6d37ac79ceeb3b.avif?t=1745087539\" width=386 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，将你的伙伴送到遇险者身边。 巴迪沿着路线行走，但途中会遇到障碍。 巴迪的双手已满，您必须替他解开谜题，为他扫清障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你成功地将巴迪安全送到了遇难者身边，那么你就可以使用担架将遇难者抬到救援点。 不过，不仅在前往途中，在返回途中也可能会遇到障碍。 有时您可能会遇到意外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/44e1955fbc2964b898698e3c35ee3f03.poster.avif?t=1745087539\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/44e1955fbc2964b898698e3c35ee3f03.webm?t=1745087539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/44e1955fbc2964b898698e3c35ee3f03.mp4?t=1745087539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/eab55d81fcf3c32be2f95b86efd0b27b.avif?t=1745087539\" width=386 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从移动板条箱和操作升降机，到阻挡湍急的水流，甚至是移动手推车，各种各样的噱头会让你和你的伙伴时刻保持警惕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >救援行动还将在独特的地形中进行，如盆地、海角、雪山甚至矿井。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/714f46b8c8ef6dd9b45f576958fbae6f.poster.avif?t=1745087539\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/714f46b8c8ef6dd9b45f576958fbae6f.webm?t=1745087539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/714f46b8c8ef6dd9b45f576958fbae6f.mp4?t=1745087539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/060493338b34c472dfdbf9a94041bc14.avif?t=1745087539\" width=386 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个阶段都会计算完成营救所需的时间，并据此确定营救行动评级。 评级越高，获得的奖励饰品就越多，可以装扮的玩家也就越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最好在所有阶段都争取获得最高评级，以获得所有装饰品为目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/977354668e3a5cd0bf4378cae31eb3aa.poster.avif?t=1745087539\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/977354668e3a5cd0bf4378cae31eb3aa.webm?t=1745087539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270510/extras/977354668e3a5cd0bf4378cae31eb3aa.mp4?t=1745087539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
